995 x11 h35 y1d4b ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">8. </div><div class="t m6c7 x14 h35 y1d4b ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">How does the Shepherd reveal </div><div class="t m171 xb9 h35 y10d8 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">the universal nature of His mission? </div><div class="t m121 xb9 h35 y1af4 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">John 10:16. </div><div class="t m1cf x27 h4 y181a ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">NOTE.—This verse underlines the breadth </div><div class="t m8a8 x3 h4 y1bb0 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">of Christ&apos;s compassion. He gave His life for </div><div class="t m3a0 xb9 h4 y1d50 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">all men, irrespective of their race or creed </div><div class="t m864 x3 h4 y1d73 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">(1 John 2:2), and intends that all shall be </div><div class="t mf38 x3 h4 y1e88 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">gathered into one common family—for </div><div class="t m695 xb9 h4 y16b8 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">&quot;there shall be one flock [rather than &quot;fold&quot; </div><div class="t m833 x3 h4 y1658 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">(see R.S.V.)], one shepherd.&quot; </div><div class="t m39b x92 h5 y1634 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Mixed Reactions to the Teaching </div><div class="t m24d x11 h35 y1bfe ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">9. </div><div class="t ma8a x5d h35 y1bfe ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">What two reactions did Jesus&apos; </div><div class="t m13a1 x3 h35 y17bd ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">discourse arouse among the Jews? </div><div class="t mfa x3 h35 y1bb4 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">John 10:19-21. </div><div class="t mc8 x11 h35 y1717 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">10. </div><div class="t m1be x74 h35 y1317 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">What later request shows that </div><div class="t m7b5 x3 h35 y1e7e ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">His hearers, though skeptical, under-</div><div class="t m2f7 x3 h35 y111d ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">stood the claims that Jesus made? </div><div class="t m121 x3 h35 y1b3b ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">John 10:24. </div><div class="t mc8 x17 h35 y1b85 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">11. <